title: The Spider 01-16 + Annual (2012-Ongoing)
description: Collects the first 16 issues of The Spider by Dynamite Comics, plus the annual. Originally created in 1933, this pulp character has long  been popular both in book and comic form as well in radio and movie serials. This incarnation, written by David Liss, will unfortunately end with issue 18, so there is no better time to get caught up then now! Also adds the last 3 issues and the annual to TPB. All credit to original scanners and uploaders. Enjoy and please seed, thanks! :-)
